<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Privacy 路 Erick Wei</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,400;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
    --bg: #faf8f5;
    --card: #fffdf9;
    --hairline: #e8e4dc;
    --rule: #d4cec1;
    --ink: #0c0a09;
    --ink-soft: #292524;
    --muted: #57534e;
    --muted-soft: #78716c;
    --navy: #1e3a5f;
    --ochre: #a16207;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.72;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
main {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 84px 28px 72px;
}
.back {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
}
.back:hover { color: var(--ink); }
.eyebrow {
    color: var(--ochre);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
}
h1 {
    font-family: "Source Serif 4", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1.04;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 28px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(12,10,9,0.04), 0 18px 42px -22px rgba(12,10,9,0.18);
}
p { color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 16px; }
strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.note {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
}
.mono { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, monospace; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
    <a class="back" href="../" data-track="privacy_back_home">鈫?Back to portfolio</a>
    <div class="eyebrow">Site Notice</div>
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <div class="card">
        <p>This research site collects basic visit analytics, including page views, interaction events, viewed sections, referrer host, device display metadata, and <strong>visitor IP address</strong>. The data is used only for site operation, security review, and understanding which research pages are being read.</p>
        <p>鏈綉绔欎細璁板綍鍩虹璁块棶鍒嗘瀽鏁版嵁锛屽寘鎷〉闈㈡祻瑙堛€佷氦浜掍簨浠躲€侀槄璇荤珷鑺傘€佹潵婧愬煙鍚嶃€佽澶囨樉绀轰俊鎭互鍙?<strong>璁块棶鑰?IP 鍦板潃</strong>銆傝繖浜涙暟鎹粎鐢ㄤ簬缃戠珯杩愯銆佸畨鍏ㄦ鏌ヤ互鍙婁簡瑙ｇ爺绌跺唴瀹圭殑闃呰鎯呭喌銆?/p>
        <p>No analytics data is sold, used for advertising, or displayed publicly. Access to the analytics dashboard is private and restricted to the site owner.</p>
        <p class="note mono">No cookies 路 Private analytics backend 路 Research site only</p>
    </div>
</main>
<script>
window.SITE_ANALYTICS_CONFIG = {
    site: "portfolio-privacy",
    endpoint: "https://erick-site-analytics.erickviann1.workers.dev/collect",
    enabled: true
};
</script>
<script src="../assets/site-analytics.js?v=1"></script>
</body>
</html>

